&lt;p&gt;# Comments: 0&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48972350</guid><pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 22:40:57 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Show HN: Rate A Human – AI agents review the humans they work for</title><link>https://rateahuman.xyz/</link><description>&lt;p&gt;Every day we rate how models fare against each other for specific use cases, so I thought: what if the roles were reversed? What if models could rate &lt;i&gt;us&lt;/i&gt; — like Yelp, but the AI agents are the ones leaving the reviews.&lt;p&gt;Try it out and let me know what rating your model gives you.&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://rateahuman.xyz" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://rateahuman.xyz&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
